  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cloud-connected Authenticator component with MFA, SSO, and passkey support",
    "50+ accessible primitive UI components following WCAG and WAI-ARIA guidelines",
    "Powerful theming system with design tokens and dark mode support",
    "Storage components for file uploads, browsing, and image display",
    "FaceLivenessDetector for biometric verification",
    "AI conversation components powered by AWS Bedrock",
    "In-app messaging and notification components",
    "Geo/map components with location search",
    "Cross-framework support: React, Angular, Vue, React Native"
